{"tid":938810,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"鼻水~在心裡流~","createTime":"2018-12-12T15:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T13:47:36.000Z","uid":52764,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f75d8aeecf994e4b9c3b1847dfb8aac294d46a1b","tid":938810,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"鼻水在心裡流　此際　怎麼開口<br />\n鼻涕在口裡飄浮　濕凍　令人太難受<br />\n鼻水在心裡流　請你咪撚開口<br />\n隨便乞嚏或隨便咳嗽　算是問候朋友<br />\n<br />\n離別秋天　自離別秋天<br />\n凍甘甘　比酷熱更難受　<br />\n太陽已失　心彷彿死去<br />\n凍死問誰可救<br />\n<br />\n鼻水在心裡流　好撚凍　問你知否<br />\n本來我用口交流　十二月溫暖不如舊<br />\n鼻水在心裡流　苦痛問怎麼休<br />\nAV打開　亦無心看<br />\n我現在似隻糉<br />\n<br />\n人像糉　我人像糉<br />\n只歎好撚凍　好撚凍<br />\n又餓又冷　心中好撚凍<br />\n口罩凍到濕透<br />\n<br />\n鼻水在心裡流　好凍　問你知否<br />\n除掉口罩交流　盼聽晚咪再凍<br />\n除掉口罩交流　盼聽晚咪再凍"},{"pid":"bb63c215b6d1b30c1d4bf98c86d0011705728adb","tid":938810,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"脾瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb234ba909a8e01dc64d07ebe154dcb60c954dd","tid":938810,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb63c215b6d1b30c1d4bf98c86d0011705728adb","tid":938810,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"脾瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:13:35.000Z","msg":"啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbcc28dd5e5023eaf3a063ee39f9fb1819a649a","tid":938810,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8a5ebbc4673d40bfae7bec968f1ef16469931b","tid":938810,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f048e12c2b1988e3089ae87a29a155464ce37a90","tid":93